shortDescription: Dream on me Hudson 3 in 1 convertible toddler bed gives your child a fun, comfortable, and colorful bedroom. This toddler bed offers a modern frame design that will blend nicely into any child's room and transition with them as they grow. It was crafted with a low to the floor design, which is ideal for your toddler to safely get in and out of bed. It is reinforced for stability with center legs and comes complete with four side safety rails for added security in radiant finishes. The dream on me Hudson toddler bed is the perfect transition for toddlers, who have outgrown their cribs but are still too small for an adult bed. The Hudson toddler bed converts from a toddler bed into two kid chairs and a table to adapt to your growing child and complement any room setting. Conversion kits, mattresses, and bedding are sold separately. Dream on me Hudson 3 in 1 convertible toddler bed meets all applicable ASTM and CPSC standards. The brilliant combination of playful colors and outstanding comfort make this bed a perfect way to enhance any child's bedroom.
